{"tid":2140859,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聯合國機密報告：朝或掌小核武技術  可嵌入洲際導彈彈頭 覆蓋美本土","createTime":"2020-08-05T09:21:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T09:26:25.000Z","uid":25558,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9a20cace7adf32a38fc556bdaceddcf5d36c4043","tid":2140859,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:21:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200805/7YEKANZ4TJ3G5NQ5CZAYXRSE5A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200805%2F7YEKANZ4TJ3G5NQ5CZAYXRSE5A%2F&d=Iz1eZ%2FSDqTYQUikxH7Zeatgc6rz%2Ba6PLwHdujBQ9FQE%3D&h=3406b24c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20200805%2F7YEKANZ4TJ3G5NQ5CZAYXRSE5A%2F&h=34a4408c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20200805/7YEKANZ4TJ3G5NQ5CZAYXRSE5A/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n聯合國機密報告：朝或掌小核武技術 <br />\n可嵌入洲際導彈彈頭 覆蓋美本土<br />\n<br />\n一份聯合國機密報告顯示，北韓未有放棄發展核武，還在不停研究小型化核武的技術，多個國家甚至相信平壤「很可能已研發到能夠嵌入彈道導彈彈頭的小型化核裝置」，並透過黑客攻擊和挖掘加密貨幣等渠道盜取可觀收入。<br />\n<br />\n路透社取得的初步報告是由一個監察聯合國制裁的獨立小組撰寫，前天呈上聯合國安理會北韓制裁委員會。報告指，多個成員。。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/kCgq7bgTFvFdAbVv_wtTzMB64yA=/190x190/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/NULTHTRV7VN5LLIUFQPTSJKSFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FkCgq7bgTFvFdAbVv_wtTzMB64yA%3D%2F190x190%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FNULTHTRV7VN5LLIUFQPTSJKSFA.jpg&h=136faf73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n聯合國報告指北韓或研發出可置於導彈彈頭的小型核武。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rl-J7CPPvJ-5_SMqyZi4XoGp9vA=/640x480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RGPUQTYBJVFWV7Y3OFZE6K7EQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Frl-J7CPPvJ-5_SMqyZi4XoGp9vA%3D%2F640x480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRGPUQTYBJVFWV7Y3OFZE6K7EQE.jpg&h=a05786ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北韓領袖金正恩與美國總統特朗普開過兩次峯會討論棄核，但暗中繼續生產鈾元素及研製核武。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/JZ1_Wqz8UYl_MFecs2SXBSa4I-s=/640x419/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/J2AUA7VH4FJZNAJQNF5FZYNY6E.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FJZ1_Wqz8UYl_MFecs2SXBSa4I-s%3D%2F640x419%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FJ2AUA7VH4FJZNAJQNF5FZYNY6E.jpg&h=f9c38440&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n南韓示威者極力反對北韓持有核武。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n核計劃未停 續產濃縮鈾<br />\n<br />\n這次並非首個指北韓已經成功研發小型化核彈彈頭的警告。一份2017年外洩的美國情報評估已指，平壤已經研發出技術製造小得能嵌入導彈的核彈頭；理論上這意味着平壤有能力把配備核武的洲際彈道導彈，發射到覆蓋美國本土的範圍。<br />\n<br />\n北韓領袖金正恩上周才強調過核武的重要，他指，在外在的壓力與軍事威。。。。。。。。。。。以配合科技改進，例如穿透輔助裝置套裝，甚或發展多彈頭系統。<br />\n<br />\n聯合國自2006年開始針對北韓的核武和彈道導彈計劃制裁當地，並持續增加制。。。。。。。。。；有一成員國更分析，平壤不用三個月便能重建並重新安裝核試所需的設施。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發動大規模黑客攻擊獲利<br />\n<br />\n聯合國專家小組另預計，北韓會繼續透過對銀行系統進行黑客攻擊和挖掘加。。。。。。。。。。。。。藉水路出口煤炭，但隨武漢肺炎疫情爆發，今年1至3月暫停了此出口活動。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/英國《衞報》"},{"pid":"acf33ad24d64385327c0d05fb7cd81623c271767","tid":2140859,"uid":61577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:23:13.000Z","msg":"有常識都知金仔唔會放棄核武"},{"pid":"a16c0499b7a37f985714940d0f9c2c2f8b8772bb","tid":2140859,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:23:45.000Z","msg":"唔洗理啦  南韓同支國咁friend  佢地會靠掂  美北友好  唔關美國事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00e1a0246c5908b982b09b171fa3aef142918076","tid":2140859,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T09:26:25.000Z","msg":"北韓射一粒導彈，D北韓人要唔要食草一年？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}